<p>LexSpecialisPrincipleinLegalCommentary:TreatmentofSecuredCreditinBankruptcy<br/>SophieZhongxianLi<br/></p>
<p> Legalcommentariesarefundamentalycomprehensive,systematicandaccurate.To<br/>accuratelyprovidescenariosofvariouspossibilities,inwhichtherulesareapplicable,<br/>writersmustproperlyaddresstheconflictwithacarefulbalancebetweenthegenerallaw<br/>andthespeciallaw.Duetotheconstraintsofgenreandlength,legalcommentariesoften<br/>failtobeexpandedindetailsonalfacts,decisionsandjudicialscenariosofthegeneral<br/>rulesunderthespeciallaw,andtherulesfortherealizationofsecurityrightsareanex-<br/>celentexamplemakingclearthelimitationsofthelegalcommentaryvision.Notonly<br/>arethelegislativeobjectivesofbankruptcylawandcivillawfundamentalydifferent,<br/>butbankruptcylawalsoplacesgreateremphasisonthepracticalutilityofprocedural<br/>rules,thenegotiationofthepartiesandthedynamicprocessofjudicialdecision-making.<br/>Intermsoflegalmethodology,thelegalcommentaryshouldsetthespeciallawasthe<br/>mainframeofreference,andmakeactionsofparties,factsandjudicialdecisionsasthe<br/>sourceofresearchmaterial.Meanwhile,commentaryfocusonspeciallawdeniesnoin-<br/>clusivenessofthegenerallaw.<br/></p>
<p>CommentaryonArticle320ofCivilCode:TransferringAccessoryThingwithPrincipalThing<br/>HUANGLong-yi<br/></p>
<p> Article320oftheCivilCodeofthePeople&#8217;sRepublicofChinastipulatestheruleof<br/>&#8220;transferringtheaccessorythingwiththeprincipalthing&#8221;,whichisthesubstantivein-<br/>terpretationruleinarbitrarynorm.Therelationoftheprinciplethingtotheaccessory<br/>thingreferstothepermanentfunctionalrelationbetweentwoormoreindependent<br/>things.Ontheinternalside,theaccessorythingmustbedesignatedtoassisttheeco-<br/>nomicpurposeoftheprincipalthingforalongtime;ontheexternalside,thereshould<br/>beaspatialrelationshipbetweentheprincipalthingandtheaccessorythingcorrespond-<br/>ingtotheaforementioneddesignation.Thejudgmentoftheprincipal-accessoryrelation<br/>shouldfolowthetradingconcept.Ifthereisanoppositetradingconcept,evenifthe<br/>twothingsconform totheforegoingconstitutiverequirements,there wil beno<br/>principal-accessoryrelationbetweenthem.&#8220;Transferringtheaccessorythingwiththe<br/>principalthing&#8221;meansthattheeffectofthejuristicactimplementedontheprincipal<br/>thingalsoaffectstheaccessorything,whichisessentialythepresumptionofthewilof<br/>thepartiesinvolved.Whenpartiesimplementadisposingactontheprincipalthing,the<br/>changeoftherealrightoftheaccessorything,inprinciple,stilneedstotaketheright<br/>ofdispositionandpublicityastheessentials.Thisarticlecanalsobeappliedbyanalogy<br/>tochangesofrealrightswhicharecausedbyjuristicacts.<br/></p>
